A '''detonation pack''' (also called '''det pack''' or a '''detpack''') was a small explosive with a remote activator that could be triggered by the user. The pack was set in place or thrown, and then detonated whenever the user desired. Typically, this was used to ambush enemies or blow open sealed doors. Some detonation packs were equipped with a three-second timer device. Detonation packs were employed by the [[Clone commando/Legends|clone commandos]] during the [[Clone Wars/Legends|Clone Wars]] to blow up heavy droid installations during raiding and boarding missions. They could also be placed on droid dispensers and walkers for easy destruction of enemy units.

